    <item>
      <title>西班牙派遣 1700 名士兵协助飓风救灾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/spain-deploys-1-700-soldiers-to-assist-deadly-storm-relief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙正在部署 1,700 名士兵协助救援工作，拯救被灾难性风暴困住的受害者，这场风暴已造成西班牙东部 150 多人死亡，目前雨水仍在蔓延至该国其他地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/spain-deploys-1-700-soldiers-to-assist-deadly-storm-relief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 20:15:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄勒冈州和华盛顿州袭击投票箱的凶手被通缉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ballot-box-arsonist-sought-in-oregon-and-washington-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[警方公布了俄勒冈州和华盛顿州两起投票箱起火事件嫌疑人的描述，目前选举官员正紧急向受影响的选民发送替换选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ballot-box-arsonist-sought-in-oregon-and-washington-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚各州拒绝 Tinubu 的税收改革，对税收计划造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/nigerian-state-governors-reject-tinubu-s-tax-reforms-in-blow-to-revenue-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚各州长要求撤回修改国家税法的立法，这对总统博拉·蒂努布增加收入以填补不断扩大的支出缺口的努力造成了打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/nigerian-state-governors-reject-tinubu-s-tax-reforms-in-blow-to-revenue-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 18:06:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班计划给欧盟领导人带来特朗普惊喜 引发担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/orban-stirs-up-concerns-he-plans-a-trump-surprise-for-eu-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维克托·奥尔班周四与唐纳德·特朗普进行了电话交谈，这引起一些欧盟官员的担忧，他们担心，如果匈牙利总理赢得下周的美国大选，他可能计划邀请他参加即将召开的欧盟会议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/orban-stirs-up-concerns-he-plans-a-trump-surprise-for-eu-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 17:46:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加州将测试选民的勇气，寻求发行 200 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/squeamish-california-voters-face-most-state-bonds-since-2006</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州将于下周询问选民是否应该再借 200 亿美元用于学校和气候变化项目，这是近二十年来该州在单次选举中被要求批准的最多数额的州债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/squeamish-california-voters-face-most-state-bonds-since-2006</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:41:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯抓住特朗普保护女性的誓言，无论她们“喜欢与否”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯抓住唐纳德·特朗普的言论不放，特朗普称，如果当选，他将“保护”女性，无论她们“喜欢与否”，以此攻击其共和党对手在生殖权利和其他自由方面的立场，以吸引郊区和独立女性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/harris-hits-trump-vow-to-protect-women-if-they-like-it-or-not</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:38:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摇摆州的印度裔美国人成为民主党目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/kamala-harris-campaign-targets-new-indian-american-voters-in-key-swing-states</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一个阳光明媚的星期天下午，两名男子在佐治亚州福赛斯县的一个街区挨家挨户走访，为民主党争取选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/kamala-harris-campaign-targets-new-indian-american-voters-in-key-swing-states</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克选举争议后准备迎接新一轮抗议活动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/mozambique-elections-country-braces-for-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[反对派领导人呼吁举行为期一周的抗议活动，以抗议他所说的选举舞弊，此后莫桑比克人正准备迎接更多的政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/mozambique-elections-country-braces-for-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 11:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普坚称自己大幅领先哈里斯，为 2024 年大选存疑铺平道路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/trump-claims-he-s-beating-harris-setting-stage-for-2024-election-doubts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普和他的盟友告诉支持者，除非出现舞弊行为，否则他们将取得压倒性胜利 - 如果选举结果不利于共和党，这将引发众怒并引发法律挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/trump-claims-he-s-beating-harris-setting-stage-for-2024-election-doubts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜发射史上飞行时间最长的洲际弹道导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-further-fueling-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜发射一枚洲际弹道导弹，其飞行时间比金正恩政权此前试验的任何一枚导弹都要长，这加剧了因朝鲜向俄罗斯派兵而引发的紧张局势。随后，美国和韩国举行了联合空中演习，以展示武力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/north-korea-fires-ballistic-missile-further-fueling-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 22:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
